Di prolonged price dey drive wedge between some franchise, and deir franchise.

Oga Morrissey, di Kentucky Fried Chicken franchise, e dey yarn sey most franchise owners must absorb di money wey dem dey pay inside di royal court, or portion of sales, sey dem must pay franchise owner.

Frankisee no fit follow join franchise price o.

But once wey franchisee agree to a promotional programme, di franchiser fit ask for full share for di very end according to Lew Rudnick & Wolfe wey be one of Chicago law firm wit franchise company client.

E say court don hold sey antitrust matter dey inside all dose kind cases because of need to protect consumers from deceptive marketing.

Any case, many franchisees, in order to stay on good terms wit franchise, routinely e dey go along with promotion.

